<p>He previously posted a video Saturday of the toddler painting at her easel, before letting out a scream, as he wrote: '#daughteralldayevryday'</p>

<p>The Boondock Saints star and Kruger welcomed their daughter back in November of 2018, after they starred together in the 2015 film Sky and began dating the next year.</p>

<p>He also shares son Mingus Lucien, 20, with Victoria's Secret Angel and Nylon co-founder Helena Christensen, 51, whom he dated from 1998 to 2003.</p>

<p>Reedus and his German model/actress girlfriend dropped $8.5million on a 1920s villa in the Hollywood Hills back in March.</p>

<p>The 7,732-square-foot, four bedroom mansion sounds like the perfect place to raise their daughter.</p>

